snippet.title: Planet Centauri - Steam Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Planet Centauri will be available on Steam on June 3rd!

You can discover the roadmap of the game by following this link:
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/updates/326292483/1453724316

Some scenes from this trailer exhibit features coming in future updates.
